        oa:exact "I guess I've seen or I think about an upgrade path as either a value-driven upgrade path or a requirements-driven upgrade path and I want to have both baked into these." ;
        oa:prefix "**Scarlet:** \"" ;
        oa:suffix "\""
      ] .

