      skos:broader narr:JargonPolicy ;
      dct:source narr:Sample_PricingTierEvolution_20260317 ;
      skos:note "Deliberate jargon policy: 'Professional' chosen over 'Enterprise' to avoid org-size connotations. 'SOW' (Statement of Work) used without definition, implying internal audience. 'BYOK', 'ZDR', 'MSA' used as known acronyms. Tier names are plain English nouns (Individual, Team, Professional) — self-explanatory without a key." ;
